headline: 5 Stocks to Watch From the Thriving Insurance Brokerage Industry
summary: The increased demand for insurance products, strategic acquisitions and the adoption of technology are likely to drive the performance of Zacks Insurance Brokerage industry players like ERIE, BRO, MMC, AJG and AON.
